title: Reliable and Worth It
content: This variety pack is great for every woman with an unpredictable cycle, its nice to buy one box versus 3 different ones to ensure you have what you need. The overall product is reliable, efficient and comfortable, the packaging is nice because it is not noisy and makes it very discrete. This box looks like it will be able to last for 3 to 4 months. Will continue to use have had not issues thus far.
